window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>How many second chances does one get in life?</b></p> <p>John wakes up in a familiar place, only to find a world that is different from what he knows.</p> <p>In order to protect those he loves, John must sift through his memories to ensure his previous ending doesnâ€™t become true once more.</p> <p>He might have brought knowledge of the future back to the past, but this time, he finds his enemies much earlier.</p> <p>How will he tell Sarah, who does not remember the love they shared or the adventures they had, who he really is?</p> <p>Old debts are repaid, and new friends are made as he carves out a familiar path to the top.</p>"; 
